Document: AudioEffectHighShelfFilter
Path: godot/classes/class_audioeffecthighshelffilter.rst
Summary: Adds a high-shelf filter to an audio bus for audio processing.

Inherits: AudioEffectFilter < AudioEffect < Resource < RefCounted < Object
Adds a high-shelf filter to an audio bus. This filter allows boosting or attenuating frequencies above a specified cutoff point, commonly used in audio equalization to shape the high-frequency content of an audio signal.
---CHUNK---
Document: AudioEffectHighshelfFilter
Path: godot/classes/class_audioeffecthighshelffilter.rst
Summary: A high-shelf filter controls the gain of all frequencies above the cutoff frequency, used to adjust sound clarity.

A "high-shelf" filter controls the gain of all frequencies above AudioEffectFilter cutoff_hz. This filter can be used to increase or decrease clarity of a sound.
